quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,137,"Kano shikali sa halali ebima biabandu bakhale."
  26,138,"Ne efwe shikhulihebwa eshinyasio tawe.”"
  26,139,"Mana nibamuyingasia, ne nikhubasishia. Toto mu kano kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibali Abasuubili tawe."
  26,140,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,141,"Babu Thamudi bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,142,"Olwa Omusiani wabu ulangwa mbu Swaleh yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsanga Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,143,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,144,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,145,"Ne shiebeenyakhwo omurungo khu kano tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi."
  26,146,"Koo, mulalekhwa nomulembe khu kali hano kano?"
  26,147,"Mumikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,148,"Nende emimela nende mitende chia ebibuli bienga."
  26,149,"Ne muyabanga mutsingulu tsinzu mukhwisangasia butswa."
  26,150,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,151,"Ne mulaloonda amalako ka ababuririranga eshichelo tawe."
  26,152,"Balia bakholanga obwonooni khushialo, ne shibakasinjia tawe.”"
  26,153,"Nibaboola mbu: “Toto ewe oli mubalia abalokwa."
  26,154,"Ewe sholi shiosishiosi tawe halali omundu butswa shinga efwe. Kho rerakhwo eshimanyisio nikakhaba mbu oboolanga obwatoto.”"
  26,155,"Naboola mbu: “Ingamia ikhasi njieino, ibe nende ebise biayo biokhunywa, nanyu mwesi mube nende ebise ebimanyishe biokhunywa."
  26,156,"Ne mulayitilakhwo khububii tawe, eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo shiaboolela.”"
  26,157,"Halali bo nibayiira, mana nibaba bokhwiyitsulisia."
  26,158,"Mana eshinyasio nishibeshela. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibasuubila tawe."
  26,159,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye owa Amaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."